# --- Heavy media (host video on YouTube / Vimeo / Releases instead) --
# GitHub rejects pushes >100 MB per file. Demo videos belong on a video
# host or under a GitHub Release; only the link should live in-repo.
*.mp4
*.mov
*.webm
*.mkv
